Thu Feb  7 22:30:51 EET 2008 (edwin)
------------------------------------
  * clamd: (bb #803)
	* don't ignore SIGBUS, SIGFPE, SIGILL, and SIGSEGV. 
	  POSIX says the behaviour is undefined if they are ignored.
	  (on HP-UX behaviour was: hang)
	* make BIGSTACK the default on HPUX 

