---------------------------------
  * freshclam: + write pid file if run as daemon (new option -p|--pid)
               + handle signals: HUP  = re-open logfiles
	                         TERM = terminate (with log message)
				 ALRM = wake up and check mirror (also on
				        SIGUSR1)


