	+ stdin scanning (uses STREAM command)


Thu Jan 23 23:51:58 CET 2003
----------------------------
  * clamd:
	+ fixed segfault with extra space between option and argument
	  in config file (Magnus Ekdahl <magnus*debian.org>)
